    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你好，战士们！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿上全新装备，展现你的风采——本DLC为你带来<strong>5款全新独家皮肤</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但这不仅仅是一个外观升级包，这是一份<strong>支持者礼包</strong>，为那些希望支持《红色至日》宇宙的玩家而设。购买此内容将帮助我们为《红色至日》、《红色至日2》以及《至日编年史：MIA》带来<strong>持续更新和新内容</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买这个礼包不仅让你更酷，<strong>更是在支持《红色至日》系列的未来发展</strong>。你的每一份支持，都将推动我们继续前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>感谢你与我们并肩作战，我们战场见！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243340/extras/8f618a9e1fbefbd69bb43851a431661c.avif?t=1750951100\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243340/extras_big/8f618a9e1fbefbd69bb43851a431661c.avif?t=1750951100 width=800 height=176 /></span></p>",
